SetMinStakeTimeConcreteUnitTest
├── When the caller is not the gauge stake manager
│   └── It should revert with {NA}
└── When the caller is the gauge stake manager
    ├── When the pool is the zero address
    │   └── It should revert with {ZA}
    └── When the pool is not the zero address
        ├── When the min stake time exceeds the maximum
        │   └── It should revert with {MS}
        └── When the min stake time does not exceed the maximum
            ├── It should set the per-pool min stake time
            └── It should emit a {SetPoolMinStakeTime} event
